title: Number of active connections to slapd instance
agents: linux
catalog: app/slapd
license: GPL
distribution: Markus Weber
description:
 This check monitors the number of current and total connection to a slapd
 instance. It also outputs the connection rate. You can set warn/crit levels to
 all three values. 

item:
 SLAPD {{Instance name}} Connections

perfdata:
 rate, Total, Current connections.

inventory:
 One service will be created for each slapd instance configured in local config file.
